name: Emmanuel THOMAS, Petitioner v. Hon. F.A. MASSIAH-JACKSON, President Judge of Philadelphia, Respondent

parties: Emmanuel THOMAS, Petitioner v. Hon. F.A. MASSIAH-JACKSON, President Judge of Philadelphia, Respondent.

opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 21st day of May, 2009, the Application for Leave to File Original Process is GRANTED, and the Petition for Writ of Mandamus is DENIED. The Prothonotary is directed to strike the jurist’s name from the caption.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.

May 21, 2009.
